{"tid":1383633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Mon Post 狗想分化我地同消防呀？","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:21:52.000Z","uid":50658,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b19d5f9153079c4f9dfa1af6036ae2250fb240","tid":1383633,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌哂你班垃圾警犬</span></span><br />\n諗住推多幾次消防唔會超過警方防線做嘢就諗住分化<br />\n個問題係你地唔撚批準人救人呀<br />\n你地阻撚住哂呀傻閪<br />\n你地唔撚阻住嘈生哂人地就唔會有咁嘅指令啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋我屌埋你地嗰堆見到個新聞衝住去屌消防深藍嘅傻仔<br />\n唔好講中上環停電所以多困𨋢<br />\n元朗嗰日幾撚多消防車出動過呀？人地有冇怨言呀？<br />\n依家個濕鳩消防大佬講句話唔會超越警方防線就割唔撚切蓆咁<br />\n咪撚咁on9啦<br />\n好明顯就係元朗消防手足做到嘢中上環先有啲咁嘅安排<br />\n用吓你地個豬閪腦啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我理撚得啲上面閪佬講乜鳩<br />\n我淨係信我見到嘅嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">消防救人，警犬殺人</span></span><br />\n就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"a077153d100dc704ff8cc3fe45cdf5d31be7e669","tid":1383633,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"香港人加油，萬事小心"},{"pid":"d4c1abfc4d63b7d43ff764d98b995680711653ef","tid":1383633,"uid":50658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"我信前線消防"},{"pid":"3bfc719ce39e32187eeb02390426770c192f7a7e","tid":1383633,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"屌你死Mon Post 狗"},{"pid":"2135fb313ba2e5a4fb02cd88e094fae047211d5d","tid":1383633,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"食屎啦Mon Post 狗"},{"pid":"a50a8849e466c974ff23d30af623afddbc60ba91","tid":1383633,"uid":258088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"一切都係警權過大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0647b500cbee783cb742e2363c75ff7ea6167a8","tid":1383633,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited